'''班伯格重排反应'''（'''Bamberger重排反应'''）是''N''-[[芳基|芳基]][[羟胺|羟胺]]在强酸水溶液作用下[[重排|重排]]为对[[氨基|氨基]][[苯酚|苯酚]]的反应。<ref name="bamberger1894">{{cite journal | last = Bamberger | first = E. | journal = [[Chemische_Berichte|Chem. Ber.]] | date = 1894 | volume = 27 | pages = 1347 & 1548–1557 | title = Uber das Phenylhydroxylamin | doi = 10.1002/cber.18940270276 <!-- currently broken for no apparent reason, has been reported to DOI --> | url = http://gallica.bnf.fr/ark:/12148/bpt6k907342/f376.table | access-date = 2008-09-13 | archive-date = 2020-10-07 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20201007204314/https://gallica.bnf.fr/ark:/12148/bpt6k907342/f376.table | dead-url = no }}</ref><ref name="os1955">{{cite journal | last = Harman | first = R. E. | journal = [[Organic_Syntheses|Organic Syntheses]] | title = Chloro-p-benzoquinone | volume = 35 | pages = 22 | year = 1955 | url = http://www.orgsyn.org/orgsyn/prep.asp?prep=cv4p0148 | access-date = 2008-09-13 | archive-date = 2013-06-07 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20130607064451/http://www.orgsyn.org/orgsyn/prep.asp?prep=cv4p0148 | dead-url = no }} ''(also in the [http://www.orgsyn.org/orgsyn/pdfs/CV4P0148.pdf Collective Volume (1963) '''4''':148 (PDF)] {{Wayback|url=http://www.orgsyn.org/orgsyn/pdfs/CV4P0148.pdf |date=20070329215308 }}).''</ref>它以德国化学家[[尤金·班伯格|尤金·班伯格]]（Eugen Bamberger，1857-1932）的名字命名。当对位有取代基时，产物为相应的[[醌|醌]][[醇|醇]]。

