''N''-芳基羟胺一般由[[铑|铑]]<ref name="oxley1989">{{cite journal | author = Oxley, P. W.; Adger, B. M.; Sasse, M. J.; Forth, M. A. | journal = [[Organic_Syntheses|Organic Syntheses]] | url = http://www.orgsyn.org/orgsyn/prep.asp?prep=cv8p0016 | volume = 67 | pages = 187 | date = 1989 | title = N-Acetyl-N-phenylhydroxylamine via Catalytic Transfer Hydrogenation of Nitrobenzene using Hydrazine and Rhodium on Carbon | access-date = 2008-09-13 | archive-date = 2012-02-06 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20120206144137/http://www.orgsyn.org/orgsyn/prep.asp?prep=cv8p0016 | dead-url = no }}  ''(also in the [http://www.orgsyn.org/orgsyn/pdfs/cv8p0016.pdf Collective Volume (1993) '''8''':16 (PDF)] {{Wayback|url=http://www.orgsyn.org/orgsyn/pdfs/cv8p0016.pdf |date=20070329200423 }}).''</ref>或[[锌|锌]]<ref name="kamm1925">{{cite journal | last = Kamm | first = O. | journal = [[Organic_Syntheses|Organic Syntheses]] | url = http://www.orgsyn.org/orgsyn/prep.asp?prep=cv1p0445 | volume = 4 | pages = 57 | date = 1925 | title = β-Phenylhydroxylamine | access-date = 2008-09-13 | archive-date = 2012-10-13 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20121013130636/http://www.orgsyn.org/orgsyn/prep.asp?prep=cv1p0445 | dead-url = no }} ''(also in the [http://www.orgsyn.org/orgsyn/pdfs/cv1p0445.pdf Collective Volume (1941) '''1''':445 (PDF)] {{Wayback|url=http://www.orgsyn.org/orgsyn/pdfs/cv1p0445.pdf |date=20070329200413 }}).''</ref>[[还原|还原]]相应的芳香[[硝基化合物|硝基化合物]]制备。

== 反应机理 ==
首先发生对羟胺（'''1'''）氮和氧的[[质子化|质子化]]。''N''-质子化与''O''-质子化的产物（'''2'''与'''3'''）互为平衡，前者容易发生，但只有'''3'''可以失水，进一步转化为[[氮鎓离子|氮鎓离子]]（'''4'''），作[[亲电试剂|亲电试剂]]与水分子结合生成产物（'''5'''）。<ref name="sone1981">{{cite journal | author = Sone, Takaaki; Hamamoto, Kazuhiro; Seiji, Yoshiyuki; Shinkai, Seiji; Manabe, Osamu | title = Kinetics and mechanisms of the Bamberger rearrangement. Part 4. Rearrangement of sterically hindered phenylhydroxylamines to 4-aminophenols in aqueous sulphuric acid solution | journal = [[Journal_of_the_Chemical_Society-Perkin_Transactions_II|J. Chem. Soc. Perkin Trans. II]] | date = 1981 | pages = 1596–1598 | doi = 10.1039/P29810000298}}</ref><ref name="kohnstam1984">{{cite journal | author = George Kohnstam, W. Andrew Petch and D. Lyn H. Williams | journal = [[Journal_of_the_Chemical_Society-Perkin_Transactions_II|J. Chem. Soc. Perkin Trans. II]] | date = 1984 | pages = 423–427 | title = Kinetic substituent and isotope effects in the acid-catalysed rearrangement of N-phenylhydroxylamines. Are nitrenium lons involved? | doi = 10.1039/P29840000423}}</ref>

